data.description: This gorgeous home on 2.57 acres is in the highly sought-after Clover Valley subdivision. You will love the engineered wood flooring with lots of natural light throughout the living space. The spacious living area has a large brick fireplace with built-ins. The kitchen has granite countertops, a large island, a spacious walk-in pantry & plenty of cabinets. Just off the living room is an outdoor living space complete with a fireplace and stunning views of this beautiful, wooded lot. The oversized master suite features a sitting area, a spacious en-suite bath, a large soaking tub, custom tiled walk-in shower. The closet is spacious with built-in shelving. The two downstairs guest rooms feature vaulted ceilings and a jack-n-jill bath. Upstairs you will find a large bedroom with a private bath and walk-in closet. Other amenities include a 3-car garage, a half bath, and a spacious laundry room. Schedule your private showing today!
